# Paths the Nx workspace scanner must ignore.
#
# Same syntax as .gitignore. The Nx 22 inference plugins (@nx/js/typescript,
# @nx/vite/plugin, @nx/eslint/plugin) walk the workspace looking for
# project markers (package.json, tsconfig.json, project.json, etc.). Any
# match becomes a project — even inside source trees where we just want
# to store data.
#
# Generator fixtures are real package layouts (captured from real tools
# like create-next-app) used as Tree-test inputs. They MUST NOT be
# inferred as Nx projects: they have their own tsconfig, package.json,
# and lint configs that conflict with the workspace's, and running any
# target against them is meaningless. Ignoring them here is what keeps
# `nx run-many` honest about how many projects we actually have.
**/__fixtures__/
